reviewText: I  AM HAPPY TO GIVE THESE SET OF DVDS A HIGH RATING,THEY ARE A VERY GOOD OVER VIEW OF THIS PRIZED AREA OF OKINAWAN KARATE.FOR THOES INTERESTED IN THIS SUBJECT IT IS MONEY WELL SPENT.

This set is fantastic!!
I have been extremely interested in the mystery of the white crane systems for a long time. This set of five DVD's gave me the depth and knowledge that I needed to fully understand this white crane system. It is a treasure of information more valuable to a martial artist like myself, than can be expessed into  words. I am thankful this ancient system is revealed at last so clearly.
